  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK603">
<l>maṭimaṭik koṇṭoḻukum pētai piṟanta</l>
<l>kuṭimaṭiyun taṉṉiṉu muntu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The (lustre of the) family of the ignorant man, who acts under the influence of destructive laziness will perish, even before he is dead.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
